OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773087076
OL,3,CMojtaba Khamenei: What does Iran's new
OL,4,Cleader say about the regime's
OL,5,Cintentions?
OL,7,FThe decision by the Assembly of
OL,8,FExperts to elevate Mojtaba Khamenei -
OL,9,Fprecisely the opposite of the type of
OL,10,Fcandidate the United States had been
OL,11,Fhoping for - places the secretive
OL,12,Ffigure at the apex of Iran's political
OL,13,Fsystem.
OL,15,FFor years, he has operated as a
OL,16,Fgatekeeper to his father, shaping
OL,17,Faccess, influence and decision-making
OL,18,Fwithin the inner circle of the Islamic
OL,19,FRepublic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773087076
OL,3,CMojtaba Khamenei: What does Iran's new
OL,4,Cleader say about the regime's
OL,5,Cintentions?
OL,7,FNo wonder he was once described as
OL,8,F"the power behind the robes" in
OL,9,FAmerican diplomatic cables.
OL,11,FIn 2009, he was reported to have taken
OL,12,Fcontrol of the militia being used to
OL,13,Fcrush a protest movement. He is also
OL,14,Fsaid to play a significant role in
OL,15,FIran's state broadcasting and
OL,16,Fpropaganda apparatus ` the same
OL,17,Fmachinery now tasked with framing his
OL,18,Ffather's death.
OL,20,FHis elevation therefore, carries both
OL,21,Fsymbolism and strategy.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773087076
OL,3,CMojtaba Khamenei: What does Iran's new
OL,4,Cleader say about the regime's
OL,5,Cintentions?
OL,7,FSymbolism, because the son of the man
OL,8,Fjust killed now occupies his father's
OL,9,Fseat ` reinforcing the regime's
OL,10,Fattempt to portray Ali Khamenei as a
OL,11,Fmartyr whose legacy continues through
OL,12,Fthe system he built.
OL,14,FAnd strategy, because Mojtaba Khamenei
OL,15,Fhas long been seen as closely aligned
OL,16,Fwith Iran's most powerful security
OL,17,Finstitution, the Islamic Revolutionary
OL,18,FGuard Corps.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
