OL,3,CMojtaba Khamenei: What does Iran's new
OL,4,Cleader say about the regime's
OL,5,Cintentions?
OL,7,FRumours inside Iran's political
OL,8,Festablishment have for years suggested
OL,9,Fthat elements of the Guards favoured
OL,10,Fhim as a successor.
OL,12,FIf so, the appointment represents
OL,13,Fcontinuity in the deepest sense: the
OL,14,Fclerical leadership and the security
OL,15,Fstate closing ranks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
