OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773087076
OL,3,CMojtaba Khamenei: What does Iran's new
OL,4,Cleader say about the regime's
OL,5,Cintentions?
OL,7,FUnder Article 111 of Iran's
OL,8,Fconstitution, the death of a Supreme
OL,9,FLeader triggers the creation of a
OL,10,Ftemporary leadership council, composed
OL,11,Fof the president, the head of the
OL,12,Fjudiciary and a cleric from the
OL,13,FGuardian Council, which oversees the
OL,14,Ftransition until the Assembly of
OL,15,FExperts selects a permanent successor.
OL,17,FThis time, however, the mechanics of
OL,18,Fthat transition reflected the
OL,19,Frealities of war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
