PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773087076
OL,3,CMojtaba Khamenei: What does Iran's new
OL,4,Cleader say about the regime's
OL,5,Cintentions?
OL,7,FMembers of the Assembly reportedly
OL,8,Fheld portions of their deliberations
OL,9,Fvirtually, wary that senior clerics
OL,10,Fthemselves could become targets of
OL,11,FAmerican or Israeli strikes.
OL,13,FIn Washington, the appointment will
OL,14,Fmake Donald Trump less likely to seek
OL,15,Fan 'off ramp' - despite encouragement
OL,16,Ffrom some of his allies in the Middle
OL,17,FEast to do so.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
