OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773087076
OL,3,CMojtaba Khamenei: What does Iran's new
OL,4,Cleader say about the regime's
OL,5,Cintentions?
OL,7,F"I guess the worst case would be we do
OL,8,Fthis and somebody takes over who's as
OL,9,Fbad as the previous person," Trump
OL,10,Fsaid on Tuesday.
OL,12,FThis appointment, in his view,
OL,13,Frepresents just that: hereditary
OL,14,Fcontinuity at the very top of the
OL,15,Fstate.
OL,17,FHe will almost certainly be considered
OL,18,Fa target for Israel and the United
OL,19,FStates.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@\O]
